<div class="about-container">
  <h1>About Me</h1>
  <p>I am a Bioinformatician at the <a href="https://chrfbd.org/">Child Health Research Foundation</a>, combining biochemistry, molecular biology, and computer science to improve human health. I specialize in developing state-of-the-art computational methods to uncover the genomic complexities of diseases and collaborate with experts to deliver impactful solutions.</p>
